headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Obey 10F Widebody (Benny’s)
content: It’s common knowledge that even the most beautiful creatures of Los Santos are half silicon these days. That’s why the perfect Obey 10F Widebody, an undeniable stunner in all departments, is eligible for customization at Benny's Original Motor Works. Plus, it packs a punch guaranteed to leave you with a deep plane facelift. Two for the price of one.
